    <stitle>10 SPEED TRANSMISSIONS FULLER RT-610 SERIES - INSTALL - AIR REGULATOR AND FILTER ASSEMBLY</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="IDcomponent" graphiccount="2">
        <title>AIR REGULATOR AND FILTER ASSEMBLY</title>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Install the air regulator and filter assembly on the mounting surface on the left side of
                the transmission. Tighten bolts securely (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f13024i4">Figure 184</hotlnk>).
            </para>
        </step1>
        <figure id="f13024i4" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic id="g13024i4" filename="../figg13/G13024I4.webp" type="webp" scalefit="0"/>
            <caption>Figure 184. Install Air Regulator and Filter Assembly</caption>
        </figure>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Install the air line between the output port of the air regulator and the tee in supply port
                of the air valve. Fasten hose with clamp at left rear bolt location on the gear shift lever housing (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f13024i5">Figure 185</hotlnk>).
            </para>
        </step1>
        <figure id="f13024i5" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic id="g13024i5" filename="../figg13/G13024I5.webp" type="webp" scalefit="0"/>
            <caption>Figure 185. Install Air Line Between Output Port and Tee</caption>
        </figure>
    </svcproc>
